### Version Update Workflow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Toml as pyproject.toml
    participant Build as Build Script
    participant App as App Bundle
    participant User as User

    Dev->>Toml: Update version = "2.0.0"
    Dev->>Build: Run build command
    Build->>Toml: Read version via tomllib
    Build->>App: Generate Info.plist
    App->>User: Display in Get Info
```

