## ğŸ“¦ Build System Architecture

### Build Tool Distribution

| Project | Build Tool | Entry Script | Output Location |
|---------|------------|--------------|-----------------|
| **4Charm** | py2app | build/scripts/build.sh | `build/dist/4Charm.app` |
| **Nexus** | py2app | build/scripts/build.sh | `build/dist/Nexus.app` |
| **Papyrus** | py2app | build/scripts/build.py | `build/dist/Papyrus.app` |
| **PyPixPro** | PyInstaller | build/scripts/pypixprobuild.zsh | `build/dist/PyPixPro.app` |
| **iSort** | PyInstaller | build/scripts/build.sh | `build/dist/iSort.app` |
| **LibraLog** | PyInstaller | build/scripts/build.sh | `build/dist/LibraLog.app` |

### DMG Creation Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph "Build Phase"
        A["Source Code"] --> B["py2app / PyInstaller"]
        B --> C[".app Bundle"]
    end

    subgraph "DMG Phase"
        C --> D["build-dmg.sh (symlink)"]
        D --> E["dmg-config.json"]
        E --> F["universal_dmg.sh"]
        F --> G[".dmg Installer"]
    end

    subgraph "Distribution"
        G --> H["GitHub Releases"]
    end
```

