## ğŸ› ï¸ Shared Development Infrastructure

### .dev-tools Directory Contents

```text
/Users/home/GitHub/.dev-tools/
â”œâ”€â”€ universal_dmg.sh              # Universal DMG creation script
â”œâ”€â”€ setup_dmg_builder.sh          # Setup script with shared config linking
â”œâ”€â”€ PORTFOLIO.md                  # This file
â””â”€â”€ _shared-configs/
    â”œâ”€â”€ .pylintrc                 # Shared pylint config
    â”œâ”€â”€ pyrightconfig.json        # Shared pyright config
    â””â”€â”€ CHANGELOG.md              # Template changelog
```

